{"tid":1803130,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇「黃色經濟圈」呢個雞棚開始見底現形","createTime":"2019-12-30T03:36:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T04:49:42.000Z","uid":28435,"like":10,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"e47a6eb066aef330e1dde7fa65e18a5e6201d024","tid":1803130,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T03:36:11.000Z","msg":"因為自己生活擺脫唔到幫襯大財團，所以大財團都要歸立做黃，列入埋黃色經濟圈，有啲戇鳩仔仲妄想到話要拉攏大財團老細參加黃色經濟圈 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住麥當勞呢啲擺到明紅色資本，但為左幫襯佢，不停搵藉口話麥當勞點平點多優惠點方便點就腳點好食，仲可以鬧返笑佢地幫襯紅店既人，話黃店做到麥當勞咁平咁方便咁好食咪去幫襯囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講到尾所謂「黃色經濟圈」又係左膠泛民和理非打飛機既玩意，幻想自己有6成黃絲經濟力可以打擊政府脅持經濟，但又唔諗下自己都實行唔到「罷藍/紅消費」，就成日諗住要壯大壯大威脅中央 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54d7436d5463b8b99f504b7089b8bb193a9eed23","tid":1803130,"uid":162954,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T03:40:16.000Z","msg":"Blocked"},{"pid":"77d12f0a75f721e868de7654f4ef642e473ea5e8","tid":1803130,"uid":154054,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T03:40:19.000Z","msg":"既然係咁就得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />政府驚閪咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5999d6726334b648491ae39f8088b11cf5eb52a0","tid":1803130,"uid":169918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T03:41:22.000Z","msg":"blocked"},{"pid":"194387b4aa17a62148a53205f1f0a46bcfbc2a49","tid":1803130,"uid":55973,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T03:41:55.000Z","msg":"點睇三毛開始見底現形<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6066b789a3a4253fbe933ac4199885292607c601","tid":1803130,"uid":13067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T03:42:58.000Z","msg":"政府開始驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a4e9f3300ee4627e1046cb434edef018e58692d","tid":1803130,"uid":321977,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T03:45:07.000Z","msg":"最ON9係以為只靠黃色經濟圈可以救香港<br />\n個個去洗錢當贖罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支那狗反對黃圈你就以為真係好大幫助，然後個個靜哂真抗爭變消費抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36ccea8f29104fae51acfd75f6c78aa354150a1e","tid":1803130,"uid":28435,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6066b789a3a4253fbe933ac4199885292607c601","tid":1803130,"uid":13067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T03:42:58.000Z","msg":"政府開始驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T03:45:39.000Z","msg":"經濟下行，根本咩鋪藍定黃都要執笠，關撚黃色經濟圈事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af5e821f193c2f52f7a3719c4f72801e954b3d4f","tid":1803130,"uid":291783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T03:47:13.000Z","msg":"請善用起底功能"},{"pid":"e493427e95bf3c21627cc151eb9581e22309e80e","tid":1803130,"uid":164728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T03:47:40.0